snippet: With Aaron Rodgers perhaps not playing at 100 percent because of a left calf injury, the Packers will host the Cowboys in a rematch of the so-called Ice Bowl.
abstract: Preview of NFC. divisional-round matchup between Dallas Cowboys and Green Bay Packers.
